title: BRIEF-Taiwan's TSMC orders equipment for T$5.63 billion
text:

* Says orders machinery equipment from ASML Hong Kong Ltd, Tokyo Electron Ltd, KLA-Tencor Corp and Nuflare Technology Inc for T$5.63 billion ($180.25 million)
